Windows Power Shell Commands



cd              = change directory
cd ..           = backup directory
ls              = show files in directory
pwd             = show directory path


mkdir           = make new directory
New-Item        = make new file

Protocol for Nancy
dnu restore     = must be run every time the .json file is changed or updated in any way.

dnx kestrel     = runs kestrel application





-------------------

using           = directive, tells Csharp our code is using a piece of code, like a class or object.
@model          = targets Razor framework, instead of Nancy
